high_descs: Head left and turn left at the end of the couch to face the white cabinets on the wall.
Open the tall cabinet, pick up the gold bottle from inside and close the door.
Turn around, head right, turn left at the white table, and walk to the front of the round black table on the left.
Put the gold bottle inside the cardboard box on the round table.
Pick up the box with the gold bottle inside from the table.
Head right, take a right at the white table and turn left at the arm of the couch to face the white table.
Place the box with the gold bottle on the right side of the table in front of the laptop computer.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a bottle on a table.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go forward. Turn left again and face the white cabinet.
Open the cabinet and take out the good plate. Shut the cabinet.
Turn around and go to the right. Go forward then go around the couch to the left. Turn right to face the coffee table.
Place the plate inside the box on the coffee table.
Pick up the box from the coffee table.
Turn to the right and go forward to the other table.
Place the box and plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a box and plate to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left then face the cabinet on your left.
Open the cabinet in front of you, take the golden piece inside and close the cabinet.
Turn left, then left again around the couch and face the round center table with the box on your right.
Place the golden piece in the box on the table in front of you.
Take the box with the golden piece from the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the white table in front of you.
Place the box with the golden piece on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place box with golden piece on the white table.
